@startuml
' Process View - Activity Diagram

start

:User uploads system docs;
:Capture metadata (doc type, owner, date);

:Chunk system docs;
:Compute embeddings;
:Store chunks+embeddings in Vector DB\n(doc_type=system);

:Load Safety & Security criteria set;

repeat
  :Select next criterion Ci;

  :Form query Qi = Ci text\n(or Ci-as-question);

  :Retrieve top-k evidence chunks\nfrom Vector DB;

  if (Evidence found?) then (yes)
    :Assemble context:\n- Ci requirement + rubric\n- evidence chunks\n- (optional) regulation context;
    :LLM judges Ci\n-> {status, quotes, reason, missing};
  else (no)
    :Set status = Unknown/Not evidenced;
    :Record missing evidence request;
  endif

repeat while (More criteria?)

:Generate compliance matrix report\n(criterion -> decision -> evidence -> gaps);
:Export report (PDF/HTML/JSON);

stop
@enduml
